item.title: “He’s probably gonna make you pay”: Kane Williamson rues Jos Buttler’s drop catch after losing ICC T20 World Cup match vs England
item.description: “He’s probably gonna make you pay”: Kane Williamson rues Jos Buttler’s drop catch after losing ICC T20 World Cup match vs England England defeated New Zealand by 20 runs at the Gabba to make a strong step towards the semi-final of the tournament.
